cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with cross-lingual word embeddings and bilingual lexicon induction. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it discusses the training of word embeddings. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with natural language processing and cross-lingual understanding. It may also fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it discusses the effectiveness of cross-lingual embeddings in bilingual lexicon induction. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it discusses the use of neural network-based models for learning cross-lingual embeddings.
